---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/PageHeader.astro";
import Banner from "../components/Banner.astro";
import Values from "../components/Values.astro";

import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import About1 from "../assets/about-1.png"
import About2 from "../assets/about-2.png"
import Team1 from "../assets/team-1.png"
import Team2 from "../assets/team-2.png"
import Team3 from "../assets/team-3.png"
---



<MainLayout title="About Aceltrim Ghana">
    <PageHeader>
        About Us
    </PageHeader>


    <!-- About -->
    <section class="section-about py-24">
        <div class="container wrapper">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="heading-secondary mb-8">How it started</h2>
                    <p class="slide-fleft">Our journey began in 2020 with a simple yet powerful mission: to create outdoor spaces that inspire and delight.
                        Over the years, we have grown into a full-service landscape design and maintenance
                        company, offering a wide range of services to meet the diverse needs of our clients.
                        

                        </p>
                    <br>
                    <p class="slide-fleft">
                        As we've grown, our commitment to excellence has only strengthened. Today, Aceltrim stands as a testament to the power of dedication and attention to detail. Our team of skilled professionals brings creativity and expertise to every project as we believe each landscape is unique, just like our clients. 


                    </p>
                    <br>
                        <p class="slide-fleft">At the heart of our work is a deep-rooted commitment to sustainability and environmental stewardship. Beyond creating beautiful spaces, we're dedicated to sustainability. We incorporate eco-friendly practices and materials into our work, preserving natural beauty for future generations. At Aceltrim, we're not just landscaping; we're crafting lasting, environmentally conscious outdoor experiences.

                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
					<!-- <Image src={About1} alt="Aceltrim Group" /> -->
					<Image src={About2} alt="Aceltrim Group" class="mb-8 " />
					<Image src={About1} alt="Aceltrim Group" class="" />
				</div>
                <div>
                    <h2 class="heading-secondary mb-8">Looking to the Future</h2>
                    <p class="slide-fleft">As part of our strategic vision for future growth, we are embarking on an ambitious plan to transition into a fully-fledged Road and Building Construction company. This expansion represents a significant evolution in our business model as we endeavor to broaden our scope and capabilities within the construction industry.</p>
                    <p>To support this transition, we are establishing strategic partnerships and alliances with suppliers, subcontractors, and regulatory bodies. These collaborations will enable us to access essential resources, expertise, and permits to complete projects successfully within stipulated timelines and budgets, while ensuring compliance with industry standards and regulations.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="mb-16">Our aspiration to become a leader in road and building construction signifies a bold step towards diversification and growth. Through strategic investments in talent and partnerships, we are poised to establish ourselves as a trusted leader in the construction industry, capable of delivering excellence in road infrastructure and building construction projects, while maintaining our commitment to environmental stewardship and sustainable practices
                    </p>
                    <p>We're not just building for today; we're shaping the landscapes and infrastructure of tomorrow.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>






    <!-- ============= section Team ============= -->
    <section class="section-team py-40" id="team">
        <div class="container wrapper">
            <h1 class="heading-secondary mb-20 text-center">Our Team</h1>
			<p class="mb-8 leading-normal text-center">Meet the amazing team behind the great work we do and continue to do.</p>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 grid-cols-1 gap-40">
                <!-- hardi Kamara -->
                <div class="team">
                    <div class="team-img">
                        <Image src={Team2} alt="Hardi Kamara">
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-text text-center mt-8">
                        <h1 class="heading-secondary mb-8">Hardi Kamara</h1>
                        <h3 class="green-text">Business Development Lead</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- End of Hardi Kamara -->


                <!-- hardi Kamara -->
                <div class="team">
                    <div class="team-img">
                        <Image src={Team1} alt="Hardi Kamara">
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-text text-center mt-8">
                        <h1 class="heading-secondary mb-8">Feshal Kolani</h1>
                        <h3 class="green-text">General Manager</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- End of Hardi Kamara -->


                <!-- Kofi Koomson -->
                <div class="team">
                    <div class="team-img">
                        <Image src={Team3} alt="Hardi Kamara">
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-text text-center mt-8">
                        <h1 class="heading-secondary mb-8"> Kofi Kwaa Koomson</h1>
                        <h3 class="green-text">Operations Lead</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- End of Kofi Koomson -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- End of team -->






    <!-- ============= Values ============= -->
    <Values></Values>
    <!-- End of Values -->











    <!-- ================ Section Banner ============== -->
    <Banner></Banner>
    <!-- End of section Banner -->
</MainLayout>







<style lang="scss">

    .section-about {


        img {
            
        }
    }



    // Section team
    .section-team {
        background-color: #FBFFE1;


        .team {
            transition: .4s;
            cursor: pointer;

            &:hover .team-img,
            &:focus > &-img {
                transform: scale(.9);
            }

            &-img {
                transition: .4s;
            }
        }
    }

</style>